name: Flower (KG)
description: His real name has been lost to time. Now, he is known as Flower. Opposite Raquel, Flower is Lady Grandia's right hand. A methodical stalwart, Flower is a force to be reckoned with. Though he prefers a softer approach than Raquel, there is no question of where his loyalties lie or how far he will go to achieve Lady Grandia's desired outcomes. This is 3/7 of the NAS123 NFTs.
